item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Namie Amuro - Style Album - FLAC
item.description:
Hello! I've been searching for this album for a while now and I just learned that apparently a lot, if not all! of her music was deleted by her publishing and so I went down a rabbit hole to find out this albums around 60$ bucks to 200$ for the 2014 Anniversary Edition. This is NUTS! I just want to listen to them again T.T

If anyone can help, I'll love ya forever lol. I'm just a poor boy trying to listen to good jams <3

Anyways, Thank you in advance
